      <title>Yandex 计划在 5 月之前完成俄罗斯撤资的第一阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/russian-search-engine-operator-yandex-extends-timeframe-for-divestment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家总部位于荷兰的公司在一份声明中表示，Yandex NV 已将完成价值 52 亿美元的俄罗斯业务出售交易第一阶段的期限延长至 4 月份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/russian-search-engine-operator-yandex-extends-timeframe-for-divestment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甲骨文因招标而面临南非政府黑名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/oracle-faces-blacklisting-by-south-african-government-over-tender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为打击腐败和滥用公共资金而设立的南非特别调查组要求国家财政部禁止甲骨文公司与政府开展业务，因为甲骨文公司称其招标存在缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/oracle-faces-blacklisting-by-south-african-government-over-tender</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
