    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司寻求下一步行动，但没有轻松的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/thames-water-seeks-its-next-move-with-no-easy-options-in-view</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的供水和污水处理公司泰晤士水务公用事业有限公司(Thames Water Utilities Ltd.)周四股东宣布该公司在现行监管制度下“不可投资”，该公司的未来受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/thames-water-seeks-its-next-move-with-no-easy-options-in-view</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:53:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bending Spoons 结束对视频平台 Vimeo 的追求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/bending-spoons-is-said-to-end-pursuit-of-video-platform-vimeo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在双方未能就价格达成一致后，意大利移动应用开发商 Bending Spoons SpA 放弃了对视频托管平台 Vimeo Inc. 的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/bending-spoons-is-said-to-end-pursuit-of-video-platform-vimeo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
